Winner of Big Brother Naija season four, Mercy Eke has revealed that she has changed a new leaf to follow a godly path. She disclosed this in a post on social media, revealing that she had a dream in which she was preaching, winning souls for God and healing people. According to the BBN star, she is already on a cleanse, as today marks the eight day of living a righteous life. [PHOTOS] BBN Star, Liquorose Celebrates New Year With New Ride My Next Big Move After BBNaija, Saskay Reveals She wrote, “Day 8: No alcohol, no lies, no sin, no party. God I need more strength to keep going but outside is already calling my names. “I wanna be different this year. Had a dream where I was winning souls for God( I was preaching and healing people).”